<h2> Welcome to SpotiGraph, </h2>
<h3>
  input a Spotify artist on the left, and a small depth (1-3 works best).
</h3><p>
  When you press search, a graph is generated of that artist's related artists.
  Each node represents an artist, and each edge denotes the artists related to
  that artist. The different colors indicate the depth on which that artist was
  first discovered.
</p>
<p>
  All artist relations are generated based on Spotify's reccomendations.
</p>
<p>
  If you search without registering, the maximum depth available is 2.
  If you search after signing in, the maximum depth available is 5.
</p>